00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,440
300 square feet, 320?

274
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:26,440
320.

275
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,440
320.

276
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:29,440
It's just free ball in it.

277
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,440
It's a little cramped.

278
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,440
How many square feet out there?

279
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:34,440
17, 18 hundo?

280
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:36,440
Oh, I think it's 18 hundo.

281
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,440
Give or take.

282
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,440
Sorry, gang.

283
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:43,440
I thought my juggling stuff was in the trunk of my car, but it's not.

284
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:44,440
Oh, no.

285
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:46,440
Do you think it was stolen?

286
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,440
I got you covered, boss.

287
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:50,440
Used to play with the parabolas myself.

288
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:52,440
Got some extra balls.

289
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:53,440
Hey.

290
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,440
Whoa.

291
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,440
Sorry.

292
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:58,440
I never touch another juggler's instruments.

293
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:01,440
You know, we're all here.

294
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:02,440
I've got the music queued.

295
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:05,440
Why don't I just do my routine without the juggling balls?

296
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:09,440
Prepare to go into the danger zone.

297
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:15,440
Oh, wow. You weren't kidding.

298
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:16,440
No, never.

299
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:21,440
Can someone please throw me a fifth ball?

300
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:23,440
If you dare.

301
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:25,440
Incoming.

302
00:12:26,440 --> 00:12:27,440
And we're off.

303
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:30,440
Remember, nothing's impossible.
